member.name: SYNCMGR_PRESENTER_CHOICE

member.name: SYNCMGR_PRESENTER_CHOICE.SYNCMGR_PC_NO_CHOICE

member.name: SYNCMGR_PRESENTER_CHOICE.SYNCMGR_PC_KEEP_ONE
member.summary: The user chooses to keep only one item.

member.name: SYNCMGR_PRESENTER_CHOICE.SYNCMGR_PC_KEEP_MULTIPLE
member.summary: The user chooses to keep multiple items.

member.name: SYNCMGR_PRESENTER_CHOICE.SYNCMGR_PC_KEEP_RECENT
member.summary: The user chooses to keep the most recent item.

member.name: SYNCMGR_PRESENTER_CHOICE.SYNCMGR_PC_REMOVE_FROM_SYNC_SET
member.summary: The item is to be removed from the sync set.

member.name: SYNCMGR_PRESENTER_CHOICE.SYNCMGR_PC_SKIP
member.summary: The item is not being resolved now but is instead being skipped so that it can be resolved later.
